# LC_PROTO — active development context

## Repos and roles

- **This folder (`LC_PROTO`)**: production Isaac Sim code. Git branch: `dev-SSTORM` (pushed to `origin/dev-SSTORM`).
- **`../prototypes/Development`**: research vault (experiments, auto-review, decisions). Not the main git repo for shipping code.
- **`UrbanSim`**: separate project; open in another Cursor window when working on metadriverse/urban-sim.

## Architecture (dynamic agents)

```text
Input -> Plan -> Apply -> Runtime Update
scene -> engine.dynamic (DynamicScenePlan) -> isaac_agents backends -> simulation.py step()
```

